21 §1109.5. Power to levy taxes, incur debt, and issue bonds
22 * * *
23 D. The board of commissioners shall provide written notice, at least thirty
24 days prior to the date of any meeting, at which the board may consider and take
25 action on a matter set forth in this Section, and such written notice shall be provided
26 to the governing authority of each of the parishes that comprise the Acadiana
27 Regional Juvenile Justice District.
